Palagi
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a European (equivalent to Pakeha)
Origin:Samoan
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:(g as Maori ng)
Notes: (g as Maori ng)	in cits below also Palangi, Pa'alagi; see also Papalagi
